name: MealWheel
0:
”Alexa, ask meal wheel”
”Alexa, open meal wheel”
”Alexa, start meal wheel”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: meal wheel
des:
Meal Wheel will look at the restuarants open now in your area and provide you with a random suggestion for a place to eat.

Just "ask meal wheel" to get a suggestion, and ask again to get some more.

Disclaimer: Any suggestions made by Meal Wheel are not endorsements. All data is pulled from Yelp (who does not endorse or sponsor Meal Wheel in anyway).
